lead_paragraph: After all the talk about staying out of the water in Rio de Janeiro, Serbian rowers Milos Vasic and Nenad Benik found themselves immersed in it on Day 1 of the Olympic regatta.

headline.print_headline: Weather Woes for Rowing as Serbs Capsize in Choppy Water
